News for version 1.0.3

Minor updates, see the ChangeLog

Version 1.0.1

This is the first official release of the ugrid_functions module. This module
adds a server side function to Hyrax that allows a user to request domain subsets 
of unstructured gridded data sets that conform to the convention described here: 

    https://github.com/ugrid-conventions/ugrid-conventions

